review_title: Apple, what else would you expect

review_text: No complaints. Same as the product advertised<U+0001F44D>
No USB C,No Bluetooth 5.2 ( only has 5.0v which is 2016 technology), No wifi 6E, No 5G mmWave capability in AustraliaFor a premium phone specifications are disappointing!
This is my first iPhone (although I have had a MacBook and an iPad for years) and I absolutely love it.
